  contains machine independant files.
 
  README   - this file
 
  doc        alpha user's guide directory
 
  alpha.versions
 
    Below is a correspondence-table  between versions of
    ALPHA and ALEPHLIB / MINI .
 
    People who want to use an old version of  ALPHA are warned that :
      - they should  also  use  the ALEPHLIB / MINI given in the table.
      - no bug fix is done on obsolete ALPHA versions
 
            Last update : 13 December  2000
 
ALPHA     DATE      ALEPHLIB   MINI  VERSION STATUS   NEW PACKAGES ADDED
===============================================================================
  100  11-NOV-1988    <89              obsolete     first release
  114   5-OCT-1992    >=140    >=8     obsolete     QMUIDO , YTOP interface
  115  10-MAY-1993    >=150    >=8     obsolete     ENFLW  , SLUMOK , PGPC phot
  116  06-DEC-1993    >=155    >=9     obsolete     GET_BP , QFNDIP , QIPBTAG
  117  15-JUN-1994    >=157    >=9     obsolete     QPI0DO , QVSRCH , NANO Read
  118  17-OCT-1994    >=203    >=9     obsolete     QTRUTH
  120  27-MAR-1995    >=204    >=10    obsolete     QSELEP,PGAC photons, MINI10
  121  12-OCT-1995    >=207    >=10    obsolete     NANO writing , QBEAMX
  122  29-APR-1996    >=212    >=10    obsolete     MC,JUL,VDHMATCH , TXTREE
  123  12-OCT-1998    >=310    >=20    obsolete     QELEP,d0,z0 new
  124  15-APR-1999    >=310    none    obsolete     MINI code is part of ALPHA
  125  17-JAN-2000    >=314    none    obsolete     Y2K: needs ADBSCONS >=300
  126  13-DEC-2000    >=316    none    Production   Track Refit ADBSCONS >=306

  ==> environment variables used by alpha
 
  BEAMPOSITION   $REFERENCE/phy/beam.position
  DBASBANK       $REFERENCE/phy/dbas.bank
  ALPHACARDS     data cards
 
 
  $ALROOT/alphannn
  ================
 
  alphannn.input |  used to build the alpha library
  alphannn.job   |  /aleph/phy/libalphannn.a , _dbx.a
 
  inc/              *.h include files
  news/             news
  enfl/ to util/    *.F source files
 
 
 
  $ALEPH/phy
  ==========
 
  contains alpha and mini libraries and various links to the
  sources.
 
  README           link to /al/reference/phy/README
 
  alpha.version    set current alpha version number = $alphaver 
 
  alpha.news       link to $ALROOT/alphannn/news/news.h
                   what has changed between version # nnn and
                   previous one.
 
  alpha.cards      link to /al/reference/phy/alpha.cards
                   an example of data cards to be customized.
 
  qmain.o          main program for current alpha version
 
  libalpha.a       link to /aleph/phy/libalphannn.a, _dbx.a
  libalpha_dbx.a   alpha libraries, version # nnn
                   the debug library is much too big ( > 30 Mbytes)
                   and is not maintained any more as of October 1998
 
  srcalpha         link to $ALROOT/alphannn
 

  miniprod         executable to create official MINIs with adequate
                   banks for LEP1 or LEP2 datasets.
                   ===> this is the version to be used since April 15 1999

  miniprod.cards   example of data cards for official MINI production
 
 
 
 
 
 
